&lt;li&gt;Prepare space required for planned production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cloning: cutting, rooting, and transplanting; clone care, watering, and feeding.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor growing conditions and review changes in humidity, moisture, and temperature and cultivation procedures to ensure conformance with quality control standards&lt;/li&gt;
