&lt;li&gt;Harvesting: cutting plants; trimming cut plants; removing flowering tops.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curing: hanging and dry-racking flowers; monitoring curing process and climate control.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operating and maintaining cultivation systems/equipment&lt;/li&gt;
